casebody.data:
Peyser, Respondent, v. McCarthy et al., Appellants. (Superior Court of New York City,

General Term.

July 5, 1892.) Appeal from jury term. Action by George Peyser against John C. McCarthy and others. For former report,-see 11 M. Y. íáupp. 631.

Argued before Freedman and Dugró, JJ.

Henry D. Hotchkiss, for appellants. John Fennel, for respondent. Dugro, J.

A careful examination of the case discloses no error. The judgment and order should be affirmed, with costs.
